author: jwross
msg: [ARIES-1034] Excessive IO when install subsystems and when initializing the root subsystem
Minimize IO time caused by writing to the deployment manifest by participating in the current thread coordination and
writing once when the coordination ends. If there is no coordination in progress, write immediately as before.
